  "prompt": "Can I download and listen to music in offline mode on the Spotify app on Volvo Sensus?",
  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2023, the Spotify app in the Volvo Sensus system allows for streaming music, but it does not support offline listening directly within the vehicle's app. To listen to music offline on Spotify, you typically need to download your playlists or albums using the Spotify app on your mobile device while connected to the internet. \n\nOnce downloaded, you can play music offline on your mobile device, but you would still need to connect your device to the Volvo Sensus system via Bluetooth or another method to listen through the car's sound system. Always check Spotify and Volvo's official sites or user manuals for the most current features and capabilities, as updates may have occurred after my last update.",
